@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.39)))
    v1 = 0.81
    v0 = wp.cos(v0)
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(v1 + 0.87) / (tmp + 0.71 / tmp + 0.15)))
    v0 = wp.cos(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
